name.ja: <ruby>電<rt>でん</rt></ruby><ruby>脳<rt>のう</rt></ruby><ruby>堺<rt>かい</rt></ruby><ruby>虎<rt>こ</rt></ruby>－<ruby>虎<rt>フゥ</rt></ruby><ruby>々<rt>フゥ</rt></ruby>

text.en:
2+ Level 9 monsters
Once per turn (Quick Effect): You can detach 1 material from this card, then target 1 Effect Monster you control and 1 Effect Monster on the field with a different Attribute and Type; negate their effects until the end of this turn. This card gains these effects based on the number of "Virtual World Gate" cards you control.
● 2+: This card can attack directly.
● 4: This card is unaffected by cards' activated effects, except "Virtual World" cards.
